title: NFL Week 17 Sunday Recap; The Playoffs Are Set! (Football 12/30)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Ryan Wilson, John Breech and Sean Wagner-McGough to recap all the Week 17 action from around the NFL. The guys discuss a wild finish to 49ers-Seahawks (4:15) which had a massive impact on the NFC Playoff Picture as well as the Eagles getting in and how the conference could play out in the postseason. Next, a focus on the AFC (59:15) as the Patriots will be playing in the Wild Card round after losing to the Dolphins and elevating the Chiefs to a playoff bye. The Pick Six Superfriends end by wrapping up the notable items from around the league in the final week of the regular season.
